examples: With ſence whereof whileſt ſo thy ſoftened ſpirit
Is inly toucht, and humbled with meeke zeale,
Through meditation of his endleſſe merit,
Lift vp thy mind to th’ author of thy weale,
And to his ſoueraine mercie doe appeale;
Learne him to loue, that loued thee ſo deare,
And in thy breſt his bleſſed image beare.
